<chapter id="util_digestutil">
	<title> DigestUtil</title>
	<para>
		This utility provides the function of encoding/decoding relevant strings using character set or base64.
	</para>
	<para>The following is explanation of the methods of DigestUtil.</para>
	<informaltable>
		<tgroup cols="3">
			<colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="2*" />
			<colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="4*" />
			<colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="4*" />
			<thead>
				<row>
					<entry align="center">Method</entry>
					<entry align="center">Description</entry>
					<entry align="center">Example</entry>
				</row>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				<row>
					<entry><emphasis role="bold">encodeCharset</emphasis>(String str, String charsetName)</entry>
					<entry>Encode the string using the input character set</entry>
					<entry>DigestUtil.encodeCharset("Anyframe Java Test", "US-ASCII")</entry>
				</row>
				<row>
					<entry><emphasis role="bold">decodeCharset</emphasis>(String str, String charsetName)</entry>
					<entry>Decode the string using the input character set</entry>
					<entry>DigestUtil.decodeCharset("Anyframe Java Test", "US-ASCII"</entry>
				</row>
				<row>
					<entry><emphasis role="bold">encodeBase64</emphasis>(String str)</entry>
					<entry>Encode based on base64</entry>
					<entry>DigestUtil.encodeBase64("Anyframe Java Test")=QW55ZnJhbWUgSmF2YSBUZXN0</entry>
				</row>
				<row>
					<entry><emphasis role="bold">decodeBase64</emphasis>(String str)</entry>
					<entry>Decode based on base64</entry>
					<entry>DigestUtil.encodeBase64("QW55ZnJhbWUgSmF2YSBUZXN0")=Anyframe Java Test</entry>
				</row>
				<row>
					<entry><emphasis role="bold">encodePassword</emphasis>(String password, String algorithm)</entry>
					<entry>Convert the string according to the relevant algorithm</entry>
					<entry>DigestUtil.encodePassword("test1234", "SHA")=9bc34549d565d9505b287de0cd20ac77be1d3f2c</entry>
				</row>
			</tbody>
		</tgroup>
	</informaltable>
</chapter>